{"tid":1764393,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"［12］本地 少女 雞蛋與羔羊","createTime":"2019-12-01T05:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T07:17:40.000Z","uid":64126,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"410c2673db2b98bb060a5dcca90acb640a27ac8c","tid":1764393,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"就快半年了 <br />\n但相信大家都唔會放棄<br />\n會繼續抗爭到底<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 光復香港 時代革命 </span><br />\n<br />\n雞蛋與羔羊 - 謝安琪<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/mysecretguarden/lvn1ka7gztho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fmysecretguarden%2Flvn1ka7gztho&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=c15279f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/mysecretguarden/lvn1ka7gztho</a><br />\n<br />\n毋忘初心<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油<br />\n香港人 反抗<br />\n香港人 報仇 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39d327a5a8219200de2c49331f20c8704799479","tid":1764393,"uid":64126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"雞蛋與羔羊 - 謝安琪<br />\n<br />\n寢室的花香　妻子的瀟湘<br />\n過去美好片段夢裡湧上<br />\n監倉的窗　鎖鏈的聲響<br />\n告訴我知往日成為絕唱<br />\n<br />\n惺忪醉過後還信<br />\n生活又如常<br />\n怎知卻中伏被騙<br />\n成為奴隸　大劫在頭上 不堪設想<br />\n<br />\nA餐雞蛋撞石牆<br />\n不怕壯烈下場　決不退讓<br />\nB餐俯首做白羊 一世困在牧場<br />\n餐券這兩張　怎麼取向<br />\n人已到了決志現場　再拖便遭殃<br />\n仍扮作昏睡　大夢裡等瞻仰<br />\n<br />\n警鐘給敲響　聲音多緊張<br />\n四處迅速褪掉舊有色相<br />\n屠刀機槍　高舉得囂張<br />\n要過去的價值成呆壞賬<br />\n<br />\n久安慣了曾迷信 福樂是恆常<br />\n怎想到昨日還有 會剎那變走<br />\n像千噸雪霜 降在頭上<br />\n<br />\nA餐雞蛋撞石牆<br />\n不怕壯烈下場　決不退讓<br />\nB餐俯首做白羊 一世困在牧場<br />\n餐券這兩張　怎麼取向<br />\n人已到了決志現場　再拖便遭殃<br />\n忘掉遐想<br />\n<br />\n一顆雞蛋撞石牆<br />\n不免碎裂斷腸　怎麼較量<br />\n一堆雞蛋望石牆<br />\n可以變做力場　繼續擴張<br />\n<br />\n今天雞蛋撞石牆<br />\n不怕壯烈下場　決不退讓<br />\n否則俯首做白羊 一世困在牧場<br />\n怎樣較理想　盡早思量<br />\n人已到了決志現場　再拖便遭殃<br />\n仍扮作昏睡　大夢裡等瞻仰<br />\n<br />\n要是有想像 漂亮"},{"pid":"52966225bdf8c52d3301b6cd2657c878f1b7e9ef","tid":1764393,"uid":64126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"BGM Credit to <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S_XJvtfj-k0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS_XJvtfj-k0&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=cb2416d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S_XJvtfj-k0</a>"},{"pid":"f0f4d5dad9613db1e18c99003fcf057c062349fc","tid":1764393,"uid":59342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:52:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港  時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"671d41f67137a208c601e2fb9a715a957fdab7b0","tid":1764393,"uid":77388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"笑左 原來你仲在生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持 煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b35788937567e9321ae0f3c7bcb1bf4317d31b6","tid":1764393,"uid":64126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"671d41f67137a208c601e2fb9a715a957fdab7b0","tid":1764393,"uid":77388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"笑左 原來你仲在生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持 煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T06:40:21.000Z","msg":"一陣尖沙咀見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1f3fa5b0dba2f0569f761afac139edf637c5ed","tid":1764393,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"好耐冇聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e12f1d4960be0090333f20203d9bfa14e042098","tid":1764393,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e1f3fa5b0dba2f0569f761afac139edf637c5ed","tid":1764393,"uid":2507,"like":